On Valentine's Day ... Say it with design!⁠
Remind Pixel, the armchair designed by @eugeniquitllet, allows to free your creative flair through decoration and personalization of the backrest by applying tiny colourful pixels made from polypropylene.⁠

On Valentine's Day … Say it with design!
For a Valentine’s day in the sign of love, Pedrali suggests Remind Pixel, the armchair designed by @eugeniquitllet.
• • •⁠
#valentineday #happyvalentinesday #designfurniture #designlife #interiordesign #designlovers #architecturelovers #architect #interiordecoration #instarchitect #industrialdesign #designlife #designfurniture #design #architecture #architecturedesign #pedrali

On Valentine's Day ... Say it with design!⁠
What better way to celebrate it than with original design furnitures able to surprise? Remind Pixel, designed by @eugeniquitllet, offers to anyone the possibility to become an artist by creating infinite patterns: a number, a letter of the alphabet, an object, or the love ultimate symbol: the heart.⁠
• • •⁠

Guests are welcomed in the lounge area of #PedraliPalaceofWonders, which is furnished with pastel coloured seating units from Buddy collection by @busettigarutiredaelli, combined with the low tables of the same collection, which contrast with the warm earthy hue of the floor.⁠ The set is completed by Giravolta wireless lightings by @basagliarotanodari.⁠
• • •⁠
project by @calvibrambilla⁠
photo by @marekswoboda⁠

Buddy Sofa, by @busettigarutiredaelli, combined with the low tables and seating units of the same collection, welcomes guests inside #PedraliPalaceofWonders.⁠ Thanks to its four different densities of polyurethane foam supported by elastic belts, it offers greater softness.⁠
• • •⁠
project by @calvibrambilla⁠
photo by @marekswoboda⁠

Soul Outdoor, one of the main protagonists of #PedraliPalaceofWonders, is the aluminium version with a seat made from shaped teak slats that is a special evolution of the original version made in bent wood and launched by @eugeniquitllet. This must-have outdoor furniture echoes the same inspiration and flowing lines, but is now made from curved aluminium tube.⁠
• • •⁠

In the central area of #PedraliPalaceofWonders there are  Lunar tables by @pioetitotoso_design and Jamaica seating by @cmpdesign, where the combination of different materials such as wood, metal and upholstery exemplifies the Italian “knowhow”, one of Pedrali’s strong points  The set is completed by Giravolta wireless lightings by @basagliarotanodari.⁠
• • •⁠

Inside #PedraliPalaceofWonders, there is an outdoor environment where the key element is Tribeca collection, by @cmpdesign, inspired by the classic Sixties patio chairs made from steel and woven cord. The Elliot tables by @patrickjouin.id, with their organic yet elegant forms, and Giravolta wireless lightings, by @basagliarotanodari, complete this composition.⁠
• • •⁠
project by @calvibrambilla⁠

In the central area of #PedraliPalaceofWonders there is Jazz seating collection, including the new chair, which is combined with Fluxo tables by Luca Casini. The harmony of shapes, ergonomics and elegance of Jazz collection converge in its light steel frame combined with the upholstered seat and backrest. The set is completed by Giravolta wireless lightings by @basagliarotanodari.⁠
• • •⁠

From 4 to 8 February, #Pedrali takes part in the 2020 edition of @sthmlfurnfair. The #PedraliPalaceofWonders booth, designed by the Milan based architectural studio @calvibrambilla, welcomes visitors in Hall A07:18. Guests are welcomed in a lounge area furnished with pastel coloured seating units from Buddy collection by @busettigarutiredaelli. • • •⁠
#PedraliPalaceofWonders #stockholmfurniturefair #stockholmfurniturefair2020 #stockholm #sff2020 #interiordesignfair #designfair #design #designinspirations #architecture #architecturedesign #designlovers #interiordesign #furniture

From 4 to 8 February, #Pedrali takes part in the 2020 edition of @sthmlfurnfair. The flexibility of modern co-working spaces is represented within the set that focuses on Temps, the multitasking Executive Chair by @pensidesignstudio. To complete the setting, Arki-Table adjustable with a height-adjustable top, which makes easier the workday in modern and dynamic offices and Boxie, the modern storage system with wheels by @archirivoltodesign. ⁠

{ #pedraliproducts }⁠
A drawer can hold precious objects as well as everyday items, to keep them safe and close to hand. In the office world Boxie, the storage system with wheels designed by @archirivoltodesign, represents order and tidiness, allowing space to be organised in a functional, optimal way.
• • •⁠

{ #pedraliproducts }⁠
Boxie, by @archirivoltodesign, is a storage system with minimal and essential lines, remarkable for its lightness which is guaranteed by a coated steel frame equipped with drawers that can be alternated with tops, both made in polypropylene.⁠
• • •⁠

{ #pedraliproducts }⁠
Designed to be configured differently according to the selected combination of its elements, and available in a range of colours, Boxie by @archirivoltodesign has been designed to fit into latest-generation offices, open spaces and co-working hubs.⁠

{ #pedraliproducts }⁠
Soul Soft echoes the silhouette of the homonymous collection by @eugeniquitllet, subtly accentuating and enhancing its comfort. The solid ash structure clasps the ergonomic polycarbonate seat, padded with polyurethane foam and upholstered in fabric, leather or simil leather.

{ #pedraliproducts }⁠
Soul armchair, designed by @eugeniquitllet,  stems from the idea of creating a seating using a blend of age-old methods and cutting-edge techniques. Sinuous and subtle lines characterize the solid ash structure that clasps the ergonomic polycarbonate seat, that appears suspended.

Soul Outdoor is the innovative and original armchair designed by @eugeniquitllet. It has an aluminium tubular frame, which ensures strenght and lightness, that clasps an ergonomic seat in shaped teak slats, almost like an embrace.
